54
00:04:17,019 --> 00:04:19,100
You're Chairman Jiang's daughter.

55
00:04:19,779 --> 00:04:21,399
Chairman Jiang is too kind.

56
00:04:21,620 --> 00:04:22,930
We'll have another chance in the future.

57
00:04:23,900 --> 00:04:24,810
However,

58
00:04:25,300 --> 00:04:26,680
I'm lucky to have a chance

59
00:04:26,700 --> 00:04:28,620
