63
00:04:37,740 --> 00:04:38,700
What is this?

64
00:04:39,140 --> 00:04:39,980
A tie.

65
00:04:40,380 --> 00:04:41,740
I hope you'll like it.

66
00:04:42,920 --> 00:04:43,900
I like it.

67
00:04:44,980 --> 00:04:46,540
I like it very much.

68
00:04:48,290 --> 00:04:49,240
Miss Jiang,

69
00:04:49,980 --> 00:04:51,720
if you could come to my room

70
00:04:51,740 --> 00:04:53,340
