75
00:05:16,210 --> 00:05:18,070
The one she is trying to kill is not you,

76
00:05:18,620 --> 00:05:19,860
but Yamai Taichi.

77
00:05:20,780 --> 00:05:21,990
There's no reason for this.

78
00:05:22,120 --> 00:05:23,590
If she dares to make a move against Yamai Taichi,

79
00:05:23,860 --> 00:05:25,460
she won't be able to get out of this venue alive.

80
00:05:25,490 --> 00:05:26,590
I'm afraid she didn't plan

81
00:05:26,590 --> 00:05:28,420
to leave this venue alive.

82
00:05:28,860 --> 00:05:30,860
