83
00:05:31,460 --> 00:05:33,180
Young Marshal, Jiang Yao wants to kill you!

84
00:05:33,200 --> 00:05:33,980
Why go to the trouble of saving her?

85
00:05:33,980 --> 00:05:34,740
Step aside!

86
00:05:39,300 --> 00:05:40,340
Miss Jiang.

87
00:05:40,570 --> 00:05:41,950
Don't be upset.

88
00:05:42,780 --> 00:05:44,500
They've already searched me at the main gate.

89
00:05:44,620 --> 00:05:46,300
Why do I have to be searched again when I come in here?

90
00:05:46,590 --> 00:05:47,970
They're all crude men.

91
00:05:48,530 --> 00:05:49,860
Not just anyone

92
00:05:50,060 --> 00:05:51,780
can enter my room.

93
00:05:52,580 --> 00:05:54,540
Besides, Miss Jiang,

94
00:05:55,010 --> 00:05:56,400
didn't you already come in?

95
00:05:58,220 --> 00:05:59,300
You smell so good.

96
00:05:59,300 --> 00:06:00,540
Mr. Yamai.

97
00:06:02,040 --> 00:06:04,380
This is the gift I personally selected for you.

98
00:06:04,620 --> 00:06:06,510
I would be so disappointed

99
00:06:07,120 --> 00:06:08,760
if you didn't try it on.

100
00:06:10,060 --> 00:06:10,770
Okay.

101
00:06:11,250 --> 00:06:12,440
I'll listen to you.

102
00:06:12,910 --> 00:06:13,700
I'll try it on.

103
00:06:29,840 --> 00:06:30,880
Young Marshal Chi,

104
00:06:31,520 --> 00:06:32,650
why are you here?

105
00:06:33,200 --> 00:06:34,040
Sorry.

106
00:06:34,360 --> 00:06:36,570
I didn't know you had another guest.

107
00:06:37,159 --> 00:06:38,640
I just want to discuss the details

108
00:06:38,659 --> 00:06:40,180
of our cooperation.

109
00:06:40,420 --> 00:06:42,110
Please forgive me, Mr. Yamai.

110
00:06:43,730 --> 00:06:44,480
Okay.

111
00:06:44,850 --> 00:06:45,920
I'll be right there.

112
00:06:46,930 --> 00:06:48,250
Mr. Yamai,

113
00:06:48,370 --> 00:06:49,830
it won't take long

114
00:06:50,060 --> 00:06:51,340
to try on a tie.

115
00:06:51,370 --> 00:06:52,380
Miss Jiang,

116
