your fiancÃ© is still waiting for you downstairs.

117
00:06:55,300 --> 00:06:56,610
If you don't go down now,

118
00:06:57,030 --> 00:06:58,420
he will come looking for you.

119
00:07:00,460 --> 00:07:02,050
I still have serious business to attend to.

120
00:07:02,260 --> 00:07:03,580
Once I'm done,

121
00:07:04,290 --> 00:07:05,410
I'll come find you.

122
00:07:12,300 --> 00:07:13,240
Mr. Yamai,

123
00:07:13,540 --> 00:07:14,430
see you later.

124
00:07:30,050 --> 00:07:31,770
If you hadn't ruined my plan,

125
00:07:32,060 --> 00:07:33,900
I'd have already injected Yamai Taichi with my tranquilizer

126
00:07:33,930 --> 00:07:34,800
and killed him by now.

127
00:07:34,830 --> 00:07:36,940
Then you'd have been full of holes by now.

128
00:07:38,220 --> 00:07:39,420
That's still better than

129
00:07:39,420 --> 00:07:41,180
watching your cooperation go through.

130
00:07:41,659 --> 00:07:43,890
Since you really don't want me to work with him,

131
00:07:44,020 --> 00:07:45,580
why don't you just kill me

132
00:07:46,020 --> 00:07:47,620
instead of Yamai?

133
00:07:48,300 --> 00:07:49,420
You said you wouldn't hurt Chi Yanzhou,

134
00:07:49,420 --> 00:07:50,700
but would kill Yamai instead?

135
00:07:50,780 --> 00:07:51,780
If we kill him,

136
00:07:51,900 --> 00:07:53,420
we can still stop this cooperation.

137
00:07:53,500 --> 00:07:54,380
Jiang Yao.

138
00:07:55,300 --> 00:07:56,620
Have you thought it through?

139
00:07:58,180 --> 00:07:59,700
If you want to kill Yamai,

140
00:07:59,900 --> 00:08:00,980
you'll

141
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:02,220
die.

142
00:08:03,920 --> 00:08:05,620
That's still better than letting the tragedy

143
00:08:05,620 --> 00:08:06,900
from five years ago repeat itself.

144
00:08:08,820 --> 00:08:10,740
I've already done wrong to Yanzhou once.

145
00:08:11,520 --> 00:08:13,050
I can't do it again.

146
00:08:15,570 --> 00:08:17,340
You can't bring yourself to kill me.

147
00:08:21,260 --> 00:08:23,270
I just think even if I were to kill you,

148
00:08:23,590 --> 00:08:25,600
Yamai would simply work with others.

149
00:08:26,350 --> 00:08:28,250
I might as well kill Yamai Taichi

150
00:08:28,780 --> 00:08:29,980
and solve it once and for all.

151
00:08:36,940 --> 00:08:38,580
Now that's at least a reasonable excuse.

152
00:08:46,510 --> 00:08:47,280
What are you doing?

153
00:08:47,290 --> 00:08:48,580
I'm giving you a chance.

154
00:08:49,140 --> 00:08:50,000
Kill me.

155
00:08:51,310 --> 00:08:52,500
At least this way, you can ensure

156
00:08:52,500 --> 00:08:53,860
that I won't sign the contract

157
00:08:54,770 --> 00:08:55,980
with him.

158
00:08:58,790 --> 00:08:59,670
Do it.

159
00:09:01,300 --> 00:09:02,340
Why are you hesitating?

160
00:09:03,770 --> 00:09:06,050
Haven't you already prepared to die?

161
00:09:09,580 --> 00:09:11,410
What are you afraid of?

162
00:09:11,840 --> 00:09:12,840
Chi Yanzhou.

163
00:09:13,830 --> 00:09:15,150
Don't push me.

164
00:09:22,290 --> 00:09:23,770
You don't want to kill me.

165
00:09:26,500 --> 00:09:28,010
So, you'd rather choose

166
00:09:28,370 --> 00:09:30,030
to die alongside Yamai instead.

167
00:09:32,860 --> 00:09:33,820
I didn't.

168
00:09:48,790 --> 00:09:50,420
Wh-What's going on with these two?

169
00:09:50,460 --> 00:09:51,970
Let's go over there.

170
00:09:51,990 --> 00:09:53,050
Don't disturb them.

171
00:09:53,770 --> 00:09:54,520
Let's go.

172
00:09:54,550 --> 00:09:56,220
-No one is allowed to come here.
-No.

173
00:09:56,260 --> 00:09:57,740
It's a once-in-a-blue-moon thing for my uncle.

174
00:09:57,770 --> 00:09:58,820
I have to go ask him.

175
00:10:09,270 --> 00:10:11,100
Since you don't want to kill me...

176
00:10:14,910 --> 00:10:16,800
