177
00:10:17,270 --> 00:10:18,120
Chi Yanzhou.

178
00:10:19,410 --> 00:10:20,870
What are you doing, Chi Yanzhou?

179
00:10:21,790 --> 00:10:23,670
To prevent you from ruining my plan.

180
00:10:26,080 --> 00:10:27,040
Chi Yanzhou,

181
00:10:27,080 --> 00:10:28,400
