189
00:10:44,250 --> 00:10:45,330
Then, you can kill me to your heart's content.

190
00:10:46,270 --> 00:10:47,880
Let me out now!

191
00:10:48,410 --> 00:10:49,440
Chi Yanzhou!

192
00:10:55,540 --> 00:10:57,950
Strange. Where did he go?

193
00:10:59,660 --> 00:11:01,270
He vanished right after coming out.

194
00:11:03,110 --> 00:11:05,100
I must find them and get the truth about

195
00:11:05,800 --> 00:11:07,790
