201
00:11:30,210 --> 00:11:32,240
Why does it look so strange?

202
00:11:32,320 --> 00:11:34,400
So, this is Chi Yanzhou's real plan.

203
00:11:35,200 --> 00:11:36,020
Miss Jiang,

204
00:11:36,340 --> 00:11:37,230
